    0.682689492137086
    >>> erfc(1.0/sqrt(2.0))  # portion of normal distribution outside 1 standard deviation
    0.31731050786291404
    >>> erf(1.0/sqrt(2.0)) + erfc(1.0/sqrt(2.0))
